PositionTracker This class is part of the Java Tools (see http://mpii.de/yago-naga/javatools).
PositionTracker.ForwardPositionTracker forward position change tracking - keeping track of several rounds of text modifications allowing to trace a position in the original text along the modifications to the corresp. position in the modified text after each round (one round=consecutive changes along the text) you need to call closeRun() before submitting more position changes from a new round, i.e. whenever you passed the string to be modified once call closeRun() before starting to run over the string again with more replacements REMARK: NOT TESTED WITH MORE THAN ONE ROUND!
